Package: elfs
Title: Evaluating and Estimating Latent Factor Scores
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given = "XXX", middle = NA, family = "XXX",
    "redacted@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "YYY", middle = NA, family = "YYY",
    "redacted@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Automated evaluation/estimation of latent factor scores, building 
  on 'lavaan'. Provide the data in wide format, column names for each factor,
  and receive comprehensive information regarding model fit, reliability, 
  factor correlations, measurement invariance, and dynamic fit indices.
